Package: mpwR
Title: Standardized Comparison of Workflows in Mass Spectrometry-Based
        Bottom-Up Proteomics
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: person("Oliver", "Kardell", , "Okdll@gmx.net", role =
        c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Useful functions to analyze proteomic workflows including
        number of identifications, data completeness, missed cleavages,
        quantitative and retention time precision etc. Various software
        outputs are supported such as 'ProteomeDiscoverer',
        'Spectronaut', 'DIA-NN' and 'MaxQuant'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: comprehenr, data.table, dplyr, flowTraceR, forcats, ggplot2,
        magrittr, plotly, purrr, stats, stringr, tibble, tidyr, UpSetR
Suggests: flextable, knitr, rmarkdown, testthat (>= 3.0.0), utils
VignetteBuilder: knitr
